column5: Looking to do some Trout fishing in the hamilton Saint Catherines area. Inbox me if you care to share some near by spots.
Southern shore of Lake O in the spring.
I hear they're running now...Port Dalhousie some have been landed
Closer, I get some off the rocks behind the radio towers on the west end of Grimsby, there are 2 dead end roads that give access to the shoreline.
